name: TravelBug

”Alexa, ask Travel Bug where I should travel to next.”
”Alexa, ask Travel Bug to suggest a cool place to go to.”
”Alexa, ask Travel Bug where I can travel to.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: travel bug
des:
Have you ever wondered, "I know I want to travel somewhere, but where to?" 

Let Travel Bug inspire your next worldwide destination! 

Learn of new ideas and quick tidbits about exciting destinations around the world, in a fun and conversational style. Travel Bug can plant the seed of your next vacation, and from there you can make it a reality. Your next adventure may surprise you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
